      "para_id": "Q000930.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , built his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar , ( and ) built his beloved divine audience chamber from fragrant cedarwood inside it ."
    }
